  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >95 New Levels: Even more beautiful pictures to color. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any Level: Start coloring wherever you like. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom Colors: Make your artwork stand out. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill Music: A relaxing soundtrack to keep you relaxed </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom In and Magnify: Get those tiny details just right.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for more coloring to past the time? Paint by Pixel 2, the sequel in the pixel painting series, allows you to relax with 95 new artworks to color. Whether you're in the mood to relax or get creative, there's plenty of vibrant pictures waiting to be colored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.poster.avif?t=1729574033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.webm?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.mp4?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like before, you can jump into any level you like and start coloring. Choose your favorite colors and switch between brush mode for those intricate details and fill mode to cover larger areas quickly. It’s all about making your art as unique as you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.poster.avif?t=1729574033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.webm?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.mp4?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel 2 is perfect for relaxing and getting creative. It’s your new go-to for a cozy and colorful past-time.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looking for more coloring to past the time? Paint by Pixel 2, the sequel in the pixel painting series, allows you to relax with 95 new artworks to color. Whether you're in the mood to relax or get creative, there's plenty of vibrant pictures waiting to be colored.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.poster.avif?t=1729574033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.webm?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/3ebc220fc45ded24ef8e61b82280a214.mp4?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like before, you can jump into any level you like and start coloring. Choose your favorite colors and switch between brush mode for those intricate details and fill mode to cover larger areas quickly. It’s all about making your art as unique as you are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.poster.avif?t=1729574033\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.webm?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2408610/extras/57851a3c643df23019f711fee45364e3.mp4?t=1729574033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p